    byLevel:{
      l1:['Construct the efficient frontier and identify the optimal risky portfolio','Apply CAPM to calculate expected returns and evaluate alpha','Build a complete IPS identifying all objectives and constraints','Identify common behavioural biases and their portfolio impact'],
      l2:['Apply Fama-French multifactor models to decompose portfolio risk and return','Calculate and interpret information ratio and tracking error','Apply the Fundamental Law of Active Management to evaluate strategies','Conduct risk management analysis including VaR and stress testing concepts'],
      l3:['Design SAA for institutional and individual clients using MVO, BL, and risk parity','Implement liability-relative and goals-based allocation frameworks','Construct and rebalance multi-asset portfolios with threshold and calendar approaches','Conduct full Brinson attribution and evaluate manager skill','Apply GIPS-compliant performance reporting']},
    skills:['Asset Allocation','Portfolio Construction','Performance Attribution','Risk Management','IPS Construction','GIPS']},
